OL,3,CWork starts on new #9m outpatients
OL,4,Cdepartment at Cornwall hospital
OL,6,FA 'ground breaking ceremony' has
OL,7,Fmarked the start of construction of a
OL,8,Fnew outpatients department at West
OL,9,FCornwall Hospital in Penzance.
OL,11,FThe new #9m unit is expected to
OL,12,Fprovide more modern, accessible and
OL,13,Fspacious facilities for patients.
OL,15,FIt could also prevent patients in the
OL,16,Fwest of Cornwall from having to travel
OL,17,Fto Truro or Plymouth for treatment.
