OL,3,CWork starts on new #9m outpatients
OL,4,Cdepartment at Cornwall hospital
OL,6,FFormer St Ives MP and Health
OL,7,FCampaigner Andrew George attended the
OL,8,Fceremony and welcomed the start of
OL,9,Fworks.
OL,11,FMr George said: "Managers confirmed to
OL,12,Fme the new build will not in itself
OL,13,Fyet deliver any additional outpatient
OL,14,Fclinics. However, I'm determined to
OL,15,Fsee more activity at Penzance, and to
OL,16,Favoid patients being required to
OL,17,Ftravel further than necessary."
OL,19,FThe unit is due to be completed by
OL,20,FMarch 2025.
